463
00:40:10,965 --> 00:40:12,884
Jika kau mau membuat mereka undur diri...

464
00:40:15,344 --> 00:40:16,220
Dia takkan mundur.

465
00:40:17,138 --> 00:40:18,389
Maaf?

466
00:40:19,724 --> 00:40:20,975
Aku kenal dia.

467
00:40:31,903 --> 00:40:33,279
Dengar ucapan Petugas Min?

