Tiba-tiba aku haus.

473
00:40:53,090 --> 00:40:54,842
Siapa yang harus kusuruh?

474
00:40:55,134 --> 00:40:56,302
Juru Tulis Goo.

475
00:40:56,802 --> 00:40:58,638
Bawakan aku air.

476
00:41:00,264 --> 00:41:01,390
